		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:list {"ordered":true} -->
<ol id="sensei-quiz-list" class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>When setting up a hosting account with a new company, what is one of the initial questions asked during the setup process?<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Whether you want to establish a new domain name</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Whether you want to migrate your existing site</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Whether you already have a registered domain name</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Whether you want to install a migration plugin</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list --></li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>How can you confirm that the website migration is successful?<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Contact the plugin migration support page</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Wait for 12 hours for the migration to complete</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Make a small wording or style change to the website and check if it appears on the page</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list --></li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>What is the additional step required when migrating a website with the existing domain name?<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Updating the Nameserver settings of the domain</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Making a backup of your site</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Installing a migration plugin</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list --></li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>
<!-- /wp:list -->]]></content:encoded>
